title: GORGEOUS FISHER ISLAND VIEW IN CONTINUUM South of Fifth!!!
posting_body: ['Beautifully furnished and perfectly maintained, this gem in Continuum on South Beach stand out above its neighbors.', 'Explore this 2 bedroom residence with a split floorplan and enticing views of the bay, ocean and Fisher Island.', 'Enter into the private foyer and entertain on the oversized terrace.', 'The combined kitchen, living, dining space is complimented by the beautiful bay views.', 'The Continuum is located in the heart of in demand South of Fifth, within minutes of fine restaurants, shops, and the famous South Beach', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
